data.description: Discover comfort in this charming 2-bedroom, 1-bathroom home located at 20615 NW 28th Ave, Miami Gardens.    The residence features a cozy living space, a functional kitchen, unparalleled convenience with a utility room with washer and dryer, a spacious driveway for four cars, and a backyard ready for your vision – be it a pool or additional living space.     Contact us now to make this dream retreat yours. Ideal for those seeking a cozy and inviting home in a desirable Miami Gardens neighborhood.
